OL,3,CEx-councillor and school governor
OL,4,Csubjected woman to seven years of abuse
OL,6,FAppearing at Newcastle Crown Court,
OL,7,Fthe 40-year-old was sentenced to two
OL,8,Fyears and seven months behind bars
OL,9,Fafter pleading guilty to engaging in
OL,10,Fcontrolling or coercive behaviour
OL,11,Fbetween August 2016 and October 2023.
OL,13,FThe court heard Ali met the woman, who
OL,14,Fhad had a strict upbringing by a
OL,15,FJehovah's Witness family, on Tinder in
OL,16,F2016 and a relationship developed.
